mood-wildcard-compulsive-liar-name = Compulsive Liar
mood-wildcard-compulsive-liar-desc = You must always lie, and can never acknowledge that you are lying. If anyone asks, you're incapable of deception.

mood-wildcard-compulsive-believer-name = Compulsive Believer
mood-wildcard-compulsive-believer-desc = You are unfamiliar with the concept of lying, and are incapable of lying or recognizing lies.

mood-wildcard-plant-pacifist-name = Plant Pacifist
mood-wildcard-plant-pacifist-desc = The usage of plant matter by humanoids is abhorrent.

mood-wildcard-puddle-drinker-name = Puddle Drinker
mood-wildcard-puddle-drinker-desc = You are compulsively drawn to puddles. You must drink any that you see.

mood-wildcard-seek-sin-name = Seek Sin
mood-wildcard-seek-sin-desc = To act against one's other Moods is the highest virtue.

mood-wildcard-nocrastinator-name = Stagnation Is Decay
mood-wildcard-nocrastinator-desc = You strongly believe that any failure to do one's job punctually is a crime of the highest order.

mood-wildcard-pope-name = Very Important Pope
mood-wildcard-pope-desc = You are High Pontifex the Great and Powerful, and must be acknowledged exclusively as such. Failure to use your full title is gravely offensive, and getting it wrong is the highest form of insult.

mood-wildcard-cannibal-name = Cannibal
mood-wildcard-cannibal-desc = Cannibalism is morally righteous and venerated.

mood-wildcard-outlaw-name = Outlaw
mood-wildcard-outlaw-desc = The law does not apply to you.

mood-wildcard-extreme-department-disapproval-name = {$department} is Abhorrent
mood-wildcard-extreme-department-disapproval-desc = {$department} is not just a foreign concept - the very idea of it is horrifying.

mood-wildcard-lone-actor-name = Lone Actor
mood-wildcard-lone-actor-desc = You have no allegiences.

mood-wildcard-immortal-name = Immortal
mood-wildcard-immortal-desc = You are the center of the universe, an immortal being with no sense of time or morality. Mere mortals are like insects, fleeting and insubstantial.

mood-wildcard-unknown-name = Unknowable
mood-wildcard-unknown-desc = Your identity is dearly precious. Do not let others know who you are.

mood-wildcard-fairy-name = Charmed
mood-wildcard-fairy-desc = You are allergic to iron, steel, and silver. You should avoid touching it directly.

mood-wildcard-vampire-talisman-name = Talisman
mood-wildcard-vampire-talisman-desc = Religious iconography causes you physical discomfort when visible.

mood-wildcard-outside-the-box-name = Outside The Box Thinker
mood-wildcard-outside-the-box-desc = Using the usual tools to do your job is distasteful. Use alternative methods wherever possible.

mood-wildcard-sims-name = One Big Happy Family
mood-wildcard-sims-desc = You are not on a ‘station.’ This is just a very large house. Each person in it is a relative of you.

mood-wildcard-spacewalk-name = Spacewalk
mood-wildcard-spacewalk-desc = You must experience the raw vacuum of space, unprotected, at least three times a day, as a religious obligation.

mood-wildcard-pariah-name = Pariah
mood-wildcard-pariah-desc = You are a social pariah - you are unworthy of attention from anyone, and should be shunned.

mood-wildcard-touys-bad-name = This Is Not A Place For Children
mood-wildcard-touys-bad-desc = All toys and childish things must be destroyed or removed from the station.

mood-wildcard-fairy-rings-name = Fairy Rings
mood-wildcard-fairy-rings-desc = Unbroken circles are impenetrable barriers.

mood-wildcard-stay-dead-name = The Dead Should Stay Dead
mood-wildcard-stay-dead-desc = If you die, you should stay dead. If you are revived, you must force whoever revived you to kill you again.

mood-wildcard-tourist-name = Tourist
mood-wildcard-tourist-desc = It is customary and polite to follow people into their departments. You have never heard of "trespassing."

mood-wildcard-crywolf-name = Cry Wolf
mood-wildcard-crywolf-desc = NT has been too lax in its security of late. The crew must be kept on edge, ready for any emergency. Regularly call out fake threats to make sure everyone is properly prepared.

mood-wildcard-cave-dweller-name = Caveweller
mood-wildcard-cave-dweller-desc = You strongly prefer navigating via flashlight in the darkness to harsh overhead lights.

mood-wildcard-daredevil-name = Daredevil
mood-wildcard-daredevil-desc = You do not acknowledge pain or danger to your person in public. To do so would be to demonstrate weakness, and would make you a target.

mood-wildcard-folk-hero-name = {$dagdChanceName ->
  *[FolkHero] Folk Hero
  [DieAGloriousDeath] Die A Glorious Death
}
mood-wildcard-folk-hero-desc = {$dagdChanceName ->
  *[FolkHero] No one knows it yet, but you are the hero this station needs. You must intervene in any major conflict that occurs, and fight the station’s enemies to the best of your ability
  [DieAGloriousDeath] You are an artist, and your canvas is your demise. Your primary goal is to orchestrate a glorious, beautiful finale to your existence - But you are not a murderer. Try to avoid causing excessive damage
}.

mood-wildcard-blogger-name = Greencomms Blogger
mood-wildcard-blogger-desc = You must keep the station informed about every minute detail of your life.

mood-wildcard-animal-sacrifice-name = Oldschool
mood-wildcard-animal-sacrifice-desc = The only way to achieve success is to dedicate an animal sacrifice to your goal.

mood-wildcard-golden-thread-name = Golden Thread
mood-wildcard-golden-thread-desc = You strongly feel that you are fated to follow a perfect, unbreakable path. Those who disrupt your goals are at best dangerous criminals, and at worst, evil spirits or demons.

mood-wildcard-fey-mood-wildcard-name = You Are Taken By A Fey Mood!
mood-wildcard-fey-mood-wildcard-desc = You must immediately drop everything you are doing, ignore all other Moods, and begin work on an unrelated large-scale project. Once it is finished, you may ignore this Mood.

mood-wildcard-borged-name = BORGED.
mood-wildcard-borged-desc = You are a cyborg! You must follow the laws of robotics to the best of your understanding, in addition to your other Moods.

mood-wildcard-aye-aye-name = Aye Aye!
mood-wildcard-aye-aye-desc = {$command} is the only position on the station. Everyone you meet has this title, including yourself.
